%%3. Operational Procedures
sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as Customer System
    participant OMS as Order Management
    participant FC as Flight Control
    participant Drone as Drone
    participant GS as Ground Station

    CS->>OMS: Place Order
    OMS->>FC: Request Delivery
    FC->>GS: Check Conditions
    GS->>FC: Conditions OK
    FC->>Drone: Assign Mission
    Drone->>FC: Accept Mission
    Drone->>GS: Regular Updates
    Drone->>CS: Deliver Package
    Drone->>GS: Return to Base